snippet.title: Payloaders Strike! - Official Trailer | Latin American Games Showcase
snippet.description: Dive into Ultima Tower and see action-packed gameplay in this Payloaders Strike! trailer for the upcoming first-person action game. Combine your gun attacks with melee punches and throws to overwhelm your opponents. Lead the rebellion against the corporation that enslaved you and liberate all of robot-kind! Payloaders Strike! will be available on PC.
